{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/20/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/20.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/20/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/20/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/issues/20/remove-unset-of-gazebo_model_database_uri"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/20/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}, "title": "remove unset of GAZEBO_MODEL_DATABASE_URI", "component": null, "votes": 0, "watches": 0, "content": {"raw": "In drcsim's `cmake/setup.sh.in`, we have this line:\r\n\r\n        unset GAZEBO_MODEL_DATABASE_URI\r\n\r\nIt was put there as a quick hack to allow the DRC kickoff tutorial to proceed without time-consuming network access on startup.  But it required manual cloning the gazebo model database into the user's `~/.gazebo/models` directory.\r\n\r\nThat unset should be removed.\r\n\r\nAlso, the underlying issue with Gazebo's access to the online model database [gazebo issue 54](https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/issue/54/gazebo-should-time-out-quickly-on) should be addressed.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>In drcsim's <code>cmake/setup.sh.in</code>, we have this line:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>    unset GAZEBO_MODEL_DATABASE_URI\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>It was put there as a quick hack to allow the DRC kickoff tutorial to proceed without time-consuming network access on startup.  But it required manual cloning the gazebo model database into the user's <code>~/.gazebo/models</code> directory.</p>\n<p>That unset should be removed.</p>\n<p>Also, the underlying issue with Gazebo's access to the online model database <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/issue/54/gazebo-should-time-out-quickly-on\" rel=\"nofollow\">gazebo issue 54</a> should be addressed.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2012-10-30T03:04:45.865795+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2012-10-30T22:05:27.401893+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 20}